node.text:
New MillVille CHOOB is live! Hope you guys enjoy. Some good bants, good throw backs some BTS & a bit of baby sitting. Cheers! (Link in bio) 
.
.

node.text:
Millville done & dusted. Top 10 is all I had to give today. 2nd moto struggled bad with my energy & strength but we got through it and will continue to recover. New youchoob drops tomorrow! Keep an eye out! On to next weekend🤟🏽📈
.
.
